getPlayUrl

public java.lang.String getPlayUrl()
If present, returns the url of the flash version of the video that can be played inline on your page. To play this video simply create and <embed> element on your page using this value as the src attribute and using application/x-shockwave-flash as the type attribute. If you want the video to play right away, make sure to append &autoPlay=true to the url.

Returns:
If present, returns the url of the flash version of the video that can be played inline on your page. Otherwise, returns null.
